1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,962
=Episode 2=

16
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,240
(Five years ago)
Li Mingxuan, it's your treat today.

17
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,760
My treat, my treat.

18
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,479
Congrats to us

19
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,639
for landing another big order.

20
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,040
Facts have proven

21
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:54,680
that our Chuxia

22
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,479
is a dark horse in the market.

23
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,040
It'll definitely be even more amazing.

24
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,919
Yes, we need to make a real impact

25
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:00,839
on this market.

26
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,760
Chuxia Business Investigation Company,

27
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,680
then Chuxia Venture Capital,

28
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,079
and then our Chuxia

29
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:07,040
will be a conglomerate.

30
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,319
A giant corporation

31
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,279
just like Lysen.

32
00:02:09,279 --> 00:02:10,080
Right, right!

33
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,800
The three of us

34
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,080
must all thank Yuci.

35
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,039
If she hadn't developed

36
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:16,120
a data analysis model
unlike any other on the market,

37
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:16,759
Chuxia

38
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,879
wouldn't exist.

39
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:20,790
It's all thanks to the little genius
of our Financial Mathematics department.

40
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,680
That's how we could start
a business right after graduation.

41
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,400
Yes!

42
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,800
And cheers to us turning from classmates
into business partners.

43
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,480
Thank you, Little Genius!

44
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,439
Cheers to Chuxia!

45
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:29,480
Cheers to the bright future of Chuxia!

46
00:02:29,553 --> 00:02:32,565
(Chuxia, Dept 1)

47
00:02:40,103 --> 00:02:45,215
(Chuxia, Investment Dept 1)

48
00:02:45,278 --> 00:02:45,719
(Chuxia, Dept 1)

49
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,800
(The three of you)

50
00:02:47,103 --> 00:02:48,543
(were once so dependent on me,)

51
00:02:49,415 --> 00:02:50,375
(yet so cruelly,)

52
00:02:50,375 --> 00:02:51,655
(you all betrayed me together.)

53
00:02:51,728 --> 00:02:53,703
(Business)

54
00:02:53,703 --> 00:02:56,263
(Investment Dept 1)
(But this world is just that mysterious.)

55
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,960
(At 26, she sold the company to Lysen.)
(Three years later, today,)

56
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:01,039
(let's start)

57
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,721
(with you, Li Mingxuan.)

58
00:03:45,265 --> 00:03:46,064
Miss Rao,

59
00:03:46,559 --> 00:03:48,080
welcome to Lysen Group.

60
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,719
This is my suggestion.

61
00:03:53,279 --> 00:03:54,400
Given your excellent

62
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,520
data analysis skills,

63
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,920
(Ren Jing, HR Director of Lysen Group)
the analyst position in the Futures Investment Dept

64
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,839
(Ren Jing, HR Director of Lysen Group)
would suit you best.

65
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:02,465
(Futures Investment Dept, Director Li Ming,
Policy & Industry Research, Trading Execution)

66
00:04:04,978 --> 00:04:05,565
(Futures Investment Dept,
Director Li Ming)

67
00:04:06,628 --> 00:04:07,540
(Investment Dept 2, VP Chen Xi)

68
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,853
(Investment Dept 2)

69
00:04:08,915 --> 00:04:09,703
(Investment Dept 2, VP Chen Xi)

70
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:10,940
(Investment Dept 3, Manager Yu Peidong)

71
00:04:11,028 --> 00:04:12,965
(Investment Dept 3)

72
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:18,659
I'll go here.

73
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,879
Are you sure?

74
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,199
Yes.

75
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,920
Be careful up there.

76
00:04:35,490 --> 00:04:37,120
Sir, look at this air conditioner.

77
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,120
It leaks every couple of days.

78
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,360
It was just fixed last month,

79
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,559
and now it's leaking again.

80
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,120
I'm checking, I'm checking.

81
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,959
Dept 2 is right above Dept 3.

82
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,800
Could it be a leak

83
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,840
somewhere in Dept 2?

84
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,280
Then, sir,

85
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,759
have you checked Dept 2?

86
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,600
I did.

87
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:53,399
Their leader said they were too busy
and didn't have time to cooperate.

88
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:53,959
Well...

89
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:54,720
How about this?

90
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,840
I'll go up and check again.

91
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:57,319
- Okay, thanks for the trouble.
- No problem.

92
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,120
Thanks, sir.

93
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,519
Tian Tian.

94
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,120
What is it?

95
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,600
The newcomer is here.

96
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:20,778
Director Yu.

97
00:05:20,778 --> 00:05:21,578
Don't, don't.

98
00:05:22,153 --> 00:05:23,593
(Yu Peidong, Lysen Group Investment Dept 3)
Please don't call me Director Yu.

99
00:05:24,165 --> 00:05:26,165
(Yu Peidong, Lysen Group Investment Dept 3)
I'm only temporarily managing Dept 3.

100
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,879
You can call me Yu

101
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,879
or Manager Yu.

102
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:34,800
How should I address you?

103
00:05:35,378 --> 00:05:36,258
Rao Yuci.

104
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,040
Rao Yuci.

105
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,240
That's not what I meant.

106
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,600
Did you bring your phone?

107
00:05:41,999 --> 00:05:42,800
I did.

108
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,559
Give it to me.

109
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,999
Why do you need my phone?

110
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:52,399
It's like this.

111
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:56,160
I am quite sensitive
to cell phone signals.

112
00:05:56,559 --> 00:05:58,199
From now on, when you come to my office,

113
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,040
either turn it off

114
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,840
or just don't bring it at all.

115
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,199
Is that okay?

116
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,720
Okay.

117
00:06:10,278 --> 00:06:11,690
(Powering off)

118
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,120
Thanks.

119
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,480
Sorry about that.

120
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:26,439
Do you know what

121
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,559
we do in Dept 3?

122
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,994
You're responsible for
all of Lysen's basic assessments.

123
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,519
Then, why did you

124
00:06:34,439 --> 00:06:35,959
insist on coming to Dept 3,

125
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,920
instead of Dept 1 or Dept 2?

126
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,240
For a certain project.

127
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,840
Stop what you're doing.

128
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:10,079
Let me introduce someone to you.

129
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,519
(Lysen Group)
This is our new colleague,

130
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,920
Rao Xue...

131
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,199
Rao Yuci.

132
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:19,120
This is Tian Tian.

133
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,120
This is Wang Meng.

134
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,160
And this is Sima Yang.

135
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,759
Let's welcome her.

136
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,199
Ms. Bai,

137
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,600
Mr. Jiang is waiting for you inside.

138
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,639
Mr. Jiang, your documents.

139
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,160
Thanks.

140
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,790
Seeing an old friend again,

141
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,199
how does it feel?

142
00:07:54,650 --> 00:07:56,399
Nothing can be hidden
from you, Mr. Jiang.

143
00:07:58,559 --> 00:08:01,399
Back then, we spent such a large sum

144
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,840
to acquire a startup.

145
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,680
Of course we had to do
some background checks.

146
00:08:06,303 --> 00:08:07,280
(Three years ago)

147
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:09,520
As the saying goes,
the new generation surpasses the old.

148
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,240
And we at Lysen

149
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,480
(Chuxia Business Investigation Sharing Conference)
have always placed great importance

150
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,999
(Chuxia Business Investigation Sharing Conference)
on new forces within the industry.

151
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:14,999
Next,

152
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:17,199
I'd like to invite
these young people up.

153
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,759
Lysen has just
signed an acquisition agreement

154
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:21,360
with the company they founded.

155
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,639
Now, please welcome them

156
00:08:22,999 --> 00:08:24,480
to share with us all

157
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,160
their understanding

158
00:08:26,350 --> 00:08:27,759
of the market and entrepreneurship.

159
00:08:28,959 --> 00:08:30,759
Then, you must also know

160
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,390
where this friend of mine

161
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,159
came from, Mr. Jiang.

162
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,120
Right?

163
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,159
Aren't you curious

164
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:40,560
about which department she went to?

165
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,360
I'm not curious.

166
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:45,360
When working for you,

167
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,840
one can't be too curious.

168
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,360
Since you're so clever,

169
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,919
help me analyze

170
00:09:03,278 --> 00:09:04,238
what kind of role

171
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,399
Li Mingxuan played

172
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:07,679
in Li Qiang's death,

173
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,440
Ms. Bai.

174
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,720
I heard that some time ago,

175
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:15,440
Li Qiang was getting very close
to you and Bai Muran.

176
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,519
Before the incident, Bai Muran

177
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:19,279
suddenly took
annual leave and went abroad.

178
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,080
Li Mingxuan manages

179
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,120
the family office,

180
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,560
yet he didn't report

181
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:25,679
Li Qiang's misappropriation of funds.

182
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,500
No matter how I look at it,

183
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,879
it seems like you all led him

184
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,720
into a trap.

185
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,240
Hello?

186
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,039
Li Mingxuan, it's been days.

187
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:54,590
So you don't want to pay back the money?

188
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,660
If I had the money,
I would definitely pay it back.

189
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,080
Even if you pressure me to death,

190
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,980
I still don't have it.

191
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,320
I've already told you guys,

192
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,120
for the overdue part,
just calculate the interest normally.

193
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,679
I'll pay it all back to you eventually.

194
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,600
How many times have you said that?

195
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,919
Do you even believe it yourself?

196
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,440
Li Mingxuan, if you keep this up,
we'll be out of options.

197
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,080
You...

198
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,039
I will definitely pay the money back.

199
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,999
Stop badgering me.

200
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,440
That's it.

201
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,600
How have your three years been?

202
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,240
Same as always.

203
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,759
And your father?

204
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,159
He's fine.

205
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,759
And you?

206
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,799
What you see

207
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,679
is what it is.

208
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:52,399
Yuci, about what happened before,

209
00:10:52,615 --> 00:10:54,120
I'm truly very sorry.

210
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,519
Do you think

211
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:57,799
saying "I'm sorry" to me

212
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,320
can just erase

213
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,639
everything from the past?

214
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:05,840
Yuci,

215
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,240
the key is that I didn't do anything.

216
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,759
You have to believe me on that.

217
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,480
You didn't do anything?

218
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:20,360
Are you sure?

219
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:26,200
(Three years ago)
Mingxuan,

220
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,480
we are friends.

221
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,519
You know I'm not sick.

222
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:34,720
Can you please help me?

223
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:37,080
Everything they're doing now

224
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,600
is just to kick me out

225
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:40,120
and sell the company.

226
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,919
I know you're my biggest supporter.

227
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,399
You're sick.

228
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,799
You need to get some rest.

229
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:57,120
Bai Liangliang orchestrated all of this.

230
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,279
I'm really not sick.

231
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:00,679
If you weren't sick,

232
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,600
why would you

233
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,279
have hurt your mother?

234
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,840
Mingxuan, I'm begging you.

235
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,960
- Haven't I helped you before?
- I know.

236
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,840
I know all that.

237
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,320
But Yuci,

238
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,279
have you ever considered

239
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:22,039
that Chuxia needs to be sold to Lysen

240
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:23,840
for us to truly

241
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,240
realize our value?

242
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,159
What do you mean?

243
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:35,080
You've known all along, right?

244
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:38,480
No, no.

245
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,200
I don't have the final say in anything.

246
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,879
"You don't have the final say"?

247
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,879
I'm just following their decisions.

248
00:12:42,999 --> 00:12:44,919
Which means you knew everything.

249
00:12:45,353 --> 00:12:46,320
You knew everything!

250
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,480
Why didn't you tell me?

251
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,990
Do you even see me as a friend?

252
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:51,919
You said you didn't do anything.

253
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:53,480
Why are you so scared now?

254
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:55,840
I'm not.

255
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:58,320
I just don't know

256
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,360
what to say.

257
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,799
We're friends, after all.

258
00:13:13,639 --> 00:13:14,840
We're friends, after all.

259
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:16,960
Where is Bai Muran?

260
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,240
He...

261
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,560
He's out of the country.

262
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:26,080
I'd really like to see

263
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:30,080
if those friends of yours

264
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,200
will actually help you.

265
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,799
I'll give you one more chance.

266
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:39,840
If you do as I say,

267
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:42,720
I'll resolve your problem.

268
00:13:44,703 --> 00:13:47,328
(Official's Mansion)

269
00:14:01,465 --> 00:14:03,304
Mr. Li, I'm here.

270
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:04,840
Have a seat.

271
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:13,200
They say white tea is nourishing.

272
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:15,799
Miss Bai, try my white tea.

273
00:14:17,053 --> 00:14:20,178
(Li Wancheng's adopted son
fell to his death due to massive debt)

274
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,399
Mr. Li.

275
00:14:31,415 --> 00:14:32,828
Before Li Qiang's accident,

276
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,639
he gave me a call.

277
00:14:36,590 --> 00:14:37,389
I know.

278
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,799
He didn't just call you.

279
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,399
He also called Jiang Dongchao,

280
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:45,360
Bai Muran, and Li Mingxuan.

281
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,279
But yours was the only one
that went through.

282
00:14:48,999 --> 00:14:49,799
You two also have

283
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:51,759
a 23-second call record.

284
00:14:55,919 --> 00:14:56,720
Tell me.

285
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,519
In those 23 seconds,

286
00:15:00,759 --> 00:15:01,960
what did you talk about?

287
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,159
Liangliang,

288
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:06,120
my dad might have found out.

289
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:06,960
If you can help me

290
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,279
talk to Mr. Jiang,

291
00:15:08,279 --> 00:15:09,519
maybe there's a way.

292
00:15:09,519 --> 00:15:10,999
Otherwise, with such a huge hole,

293
00:15:10,999 --> 00:15:12,720
my only choice is to die.

294
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:13,639
Sounds like

295
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,120
that was the simplest

296
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,240
solution.

297
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:31,799
Li Qiang did indeed
speak with me on the phone.

298
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,320
He told me

299
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,720
he couldn't find Mr. Jiang.

300
00:15:36,999 --> 00:15:38,200
He was very agitated

301
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,240
and asked me to help find Mr. Jiang.

302
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:42,240
I kept trying to persuade him

303
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,320
to stay calm and not do anything rash.

304
00:15:44,759 --> 00:15:46,200
But I really never expected

305
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,879
that next, he would...

306
00:15:51,315 --> 00:15:52,799
Are you suggesting

307
00:15:54,759 --> 00:15:55,799
that Li Qiang's death

308
00:15:55,799 --> 00:15:57,720
has something to do with Jiang Dongchao?

309
00:15:59,999 --> 00:16:01,840
I'm merely stating the facts.

310
00:16:03,039 --> 00:16:04,679
They say he was my adopted son,

311
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,960
but also my pawn.

312
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:08,080
My son just died

313
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,720
for no rhyme or reason.

314
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:13,200
Shouldn't someone in Lysen

315
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,679
be held responsible for this?

316
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,200
I heard of one thing.

317
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:24,399
Jiang Dongchao

318
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,639
met with Li Qiang privately

319
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:29,999
right before he died.

320
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,600
Miss Bai,

321
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:44,480
you are very clever.

322
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,039
Mr. Li, you've already reminded me.

323
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,799
My choice is very clear.

324
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:57,120
It's always been Lysen and you, Mr. Li.

325
00:17:05,628 --> 00:17:07,890
(Mingri Fortune Microcredit Company)

326
00:17:14,353 --> 00:17:16,053
(Huaqianba Credit)

327
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:20,753
(Huaqianba Credit)

328
00:17:23,353 --> 00:17:24,228
(Li Mingxuan)

329
00:17:41,603 --> 00:17:43,284
13.05 million.

330
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:46,479
Your debt plus compound interest

331
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:48,520
totals 13.05 million.

332
00:17:49,439 --> 00:17:50,159
This week

333
00:17:50,159 --> 00:17:51,520
is your final repayment deadline.

334
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:53,320
Can you handle this yourself?

335
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,280
This is my own business.

336
00:17:54,290 --> 00:17:55,199
I'll handle it.

337
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,600
I can help you solve it.

338
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:06,603
(Huaqianba Credit)

339
00:18:12,653 --> 00:18:17,728
(Mingri Fortune Microcredit Company)

340
00:18:23,703 --> 00:18:26,315
(Non-Local Bank,
Available Balance: 1,050,298.04)

341
00:18:30,399 --> 00:18:31,879
To show my sincerity,

342
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,239
I can transfer

343
00:18:34,239 --> 00:18:35,320
1.05 million to you first.

344
00:18:36,399 --> 00:18:38,199
You want to use me as a pawn?

345
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:42,280
What do you need me to do?

346
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,360
Ms. Bai.

347
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:14,479
Liangliang,

348
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:17,040
there's something I want to tell you.

349
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:19,320
You said last time that Mr. Jiang
met with Li Qiang.

350
00:19:19,628 --> 00:19:21,428
You're the only one who saw it, right?

351
00:19:23,239 --> 00:19:24,040
Right.

352
00:19:24,719 --> 00:19:25,560
And every time,

353
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:27,239
Mr. Jiang asked me to step out first.

354
00:19:27,239 --> 00:19:28,280
You know Rao Yuci

355
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,199
joined Lysen, right?

356
00:19:30,399 --> 00:19:31,600
Whether Rao Yuci joins or not

357
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:32,639
is none of my concern.

358
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,239
Liangliang, can you please just
fix my problem first?

359
00:19:39,239 --> 00:19:40,639
Helping me fix my problem

360
00:19:40,719 --> 00:19:42,120
is how yours gets fixed.

361
00:19:53,653 --> 00:19:55,545
I need you to do something for me.

362
00:19:57,199 --> 00:19:58,800
The board meeting is in a few days.

363
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:00,800
I want you to find

364
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,040
the right moment

365
00:20:02,690 --> 00:20:04,439
to announce something publicly.

366
00:20:06,679 --> 00:20:07,600
Announce what?

367
00:20:09,399 --> 00:20:10,639
That while Mr. Jiang knew

368
00:20:10,639 --> 00:20:12,439
Li Qiang had a gambling problem,

369
00:20:12,903 --> 00:20:14,520
he signaled that he could

370
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:16,239
freely move money
from the family office,

371
00:20:16,239 --> 00:20:18,120
and he demanded your full cooperation.

372
00:20:19,199 --> 00:20:21,040
That's what led to Li Qiang's death.

373
00:20:25,399 --> 00:20:27,520
You're asking me to frame Mr. Jiang.

374
00:20:29,199 --> 00:20:30,199
Liangliang, you know

375
00:20:30,199 --> 00:20:31,360
what kind of man Mr. Jiang is.

376
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:33,080
If he finds out I sabotaged him,

377
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:34,239
he won't let me off.

378
00:20:34,239 --> 00:20:35,879
The loan sharks
won't let you off either.

379
00:20:36,479 --> 00:20:38,120
It's a dead end either way.

380
00:20:38,719 --> 00:20:39,800
Burn your bridges.

381
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,239
You help me,

382
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:42,719
and I'll help you.

383
00:20:50,015 --> 00:20:51,415
We're friends.

384
00:20:51,628 --> 00:20:53,628
You can't push me into the fire!

385
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:55,340
If he finds out I betrayed him...

386
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:57,461
You have to choose
if you want to survive.

387
00:20:57,461 --> 00:20:58,221
Li Mingxuan,

388
00:20:58,328 --> 00:21:00,649
don't forget,
you've always been this way.

389
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:06,540
(Three years ago)

390
00:21:15,465 --> 00:21:22,959
(Chuxia)

391
00:21:22,959 --> 00:21:23,760
Bai Liangliang,

392
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,840
do you know what you're doing?

393
00:21:30,959 --> 00:21:31,800
So you saw it?

394
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:34,800
I thought you knew already.

395
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,320
Yuci is your friend.

396
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:37,800
How could you...

397
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:39,239
Yuci is your friend, too.

398
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:41,280
You can choose to tell her.

399
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:44,120
Bai Muran is backed by Baiye.

400
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,399
And I'm backed by Bai Muran.

401
00:21:47,159 --> 00:21:48,719
We started this company together

402
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,000
just to exploit

403
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,360
Rao Yuci's talents.

404
00:21:53,679 --> 00:21:54,479
Go ahead and call.

405
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:55,719
If that call goes through,

406
00:21:55,719 --> 00:21:57,199
(Phone, Rao Yuci)
you'll have two more enemies.

407
00:21:57,199 --> 00:21:58,940
(Phone, Rao Yuci)

408
00:22:04,515 --> 00:22:06,053
(Phone, Rao Yuci)

409
00:22:09,399 --> 00:22:10,199
Li Mingxuan,

410
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:12,399
congratulations.

411
00:22:13,490 --> 00:22:15,730
You've made the right choice.

412
00:22:18,239 --> 00:22:20,239
This is how you protect yourself.

413
00:22:20,959 --> 00:22:21,760
Back then,

414
00:22:22,253 --> 00:22:24,293
when you chose
to follow Bai Muran and me,

415
00:22:24,293 --> 00:22:26,278
you betrayed Rao Yuci.

416
00:22:27,639 --> 00:22:28,439
Today,

417
00:22:28,678 --> 00:22:30,853
it's just making you choose once more.

418
00:22:35,465 --> 00:22:37,120
As long as you do this

419
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:38,439
before the board meeting

420
00:22:38,803 --> 00:22:40,803
and cause enough of a PR crisis,

421
00:22:41,320 --> 00:22:43,320
Mr. Li will use it as leverage

422
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:45,800
to suspend Jiang Dongchao
from his position.

423
00:22:47,740 --> 00:22:49,379
Then, I'll have the chance to move up.

424
00:22:50,040 --> 00:22:51,399
When that time comes,

425
00:22:51,399 --> 00:22:52,800
problems will no longer be problems.

426
00:22:59,879 --> 00:23:02,159
Mr. Li is currently focused

427
00:23:02,159 --> 00:23:03,639
on bringing down Jiang Dongchao.

428
00:23:04,399 --> 00:23:05,199
If you help him

429
00:23:05,199 --> 00:23:06,520
with this,

430
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,439
just think

431
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:10,159
how Mr. Li will reward you.

432
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:14,919
Mingxuan,

433
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,399
those debts you owe,

434
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:19,120
I can help you pay them all off.

435
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,360
Once Jiang Dongchao is kicked out,

436
00:23:22,719 --> 00:23:24,959
the one who will rise with me is you.

437
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:26,879
Investment Dept 1 will be yours.

438
00:23:26,879 --> 00:23:28,199
This office and that seat,

439
00:23:28,199 --> 00:23:29,719
they'll belong to you, Li Mingxuan.

440
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,560
As for what comes next,

441
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:38,320
think about it carefully.

442
00:23:52,928 --> 00:23:55,878
(Rao Yuci)

443
00:23:56,515 --> 00:23:58,159
(I want to replace Jiang Dongchao)

444
00:23:58,639 --> 00:24:00,360
(just like I replaced Rao Yuci)

445
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:02,040
(three years ago.)

446
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,639
You also know

447
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:07,790
about the shareholder letter
to dismiss me, right?

448
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:09,439
I thought

449
00:24:09,439 --> 00:24:10,800
it was just a company rumor.

450
00:24:11,639 --> 00:24:12,439
Besides,

451
00:24:13,239 --> 00:24:14,800
Lysen also belongs to Mr. Li.

452
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:17,600
He has no reason
to destroy his own company, right?

453
00:24:18,479 --> 00:24:19,919
I think it must have been done

454
00:24:19,919 --> 00:24:21,399
by Lysen's competitors.

455
00:24:24,719 --> 00:24:25,840
With the joint-stock reform,

456
00:24:26,959 --> 00:24:28,080
equity has been diluted.

457
00:24:29,220 --> 00:24:31,380
The money Li Wancheng gets
is becoming less and less.

458
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:32,840
He thinks it's the result

459
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,800
of my management.

460
00:24:34,639 --> 00:24:35,439
In reality,

461
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:38,679
he's reaping what he sowed,

462
00:24:40,199 --> 00:24:41,690
causing the market value to evaporate.

463
00:24:43,439 --> 00:24:44,239
So,

464
00:24:45,150 --> 00:24:47,040
he wants to use
public opinion to force me out.

465
00:24:49,639 --> 00:24:51,040
So, what you mean is...

466
00:24:51,879 --> 00:24:53,040
Rao Yuci you recruited

467
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:53,840
into the company

468
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:58,439
might be the key
to breaking the deadlock.

469
00:25:05,439 --> 00:25:06,239
Mr. Yu.

470
00:25:07,959 --> 00:25:09,679
Isn't it cold with the A/C on so high?

471
00:25:19,078 --> 00:25:20,703
(Power off)

472
00:25:24,199 --> 00:25:25,120
Is that necessary?

473
00:25:26,479 --> 00:25:27,760
You have no idea.

474
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,439
That damn recording last time

475
00:25:29,439 --> 00:25:31,560
got me investigated by the company
for half a month.

476
00:25:31,879 --> 00:25:33,040
(Clicking power off)
Mr. Jiang almost made me

477
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,520
get the heck out of Lysen.

478
00:25:35,399 --> 00:25:37,760
But aren't you still
staying at Lysen just fine?

479
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,360
What's so fine about it?

480
00:25:40,199 --> 00:25:42,000
I'm a macro analyst,

481
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:44,360
yet I was demoted from Dept 1
all the way down to Dept 3.

482
00:25:44,370 --> 00:25:46,870
Every day I'm stuck watching over
those three junior analysts.

483
00:25:47,679 --> 00:25:49,600
How's that new girl?

484
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,159
Rao Yuci, right?

485
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:56,919
I feel like she's being

486
00:25:56,919 --> 00:25:58,199
a bit cryptic.

487
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:01,660
She asked for this project
as soon as she arrived.

488
00:26:03,303 --> 00:26:05,878
(Dada Wine Industry Project Report)

489
00:26:08,639 --> 00:26:10,360
Then why do you insist

490
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:11,760
on the Dada Wine Industry project?

491
00:26:14,719 --> 00:26:15,760
Personal preference.

492
00:26:17,399 --> 00:26:19,040
Or you could understand it

493
00:26:21,040 --> 00:26:22,439
as me targeting a specific person.

494
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:26,360
I recall this project was brought

495
00:26:27,370 --> 00:26:29,520
to the company
by Liu Yang from Zhaohui Private Equity

496
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,520
through you, right?

497
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,320
And then?

498
00:26:32,719 --> 00:26:33,840
And then, this is a project

499
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:35,080
from Mr. Jiang's hometown.

500
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:36,800
We're doing the basic analysis.

501
00:26:37,320 --> 00:26:38,120
Get to the point.

502
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:38,503
(Dada Wine Industry Project Report)

503
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:40,719
The point is that Mr. Jiang's
current attitude toward this project

504
00:26:40,719 --> 00:26:42,600
doesn't seem very clear.

505
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:45,280
Now that Rao Yuci
wants to take over this project,

506
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:47,040
I'm not sure if she's trying

507
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:50,399
to give Mr. Jiang another hand.

508
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:52,399
But then I thought,

509
00:26:52,399 --> 00:26:53,719
this project was brought in

510
00:26:53,853 --> 00:26:55,734
by you, after all, right?

511
00:26:58,679 --> 00:26:59,840
You are the one

512
00:26:59,840 --> 00:27:01,040
Mr. Jiang values most.

513
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,159
I'm just here out of kindness

514
00:27:03,915 --> 00:27:06,190
to give a friendly heads-up.

515
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:11,399
It's all for Lysen.

516
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:13,239
It's the same
no matter who helps Mr. Jiang.

517
00:27:13,479 --> 00:27:14,959
Mr. Yu, you're overthinking it.

518
00:27:17,090 --> 00:27:18,919
That's why people say
you're magnanimous.

519
00:27:23,215 --> 00:27:25,120
Liu Yang is my senior.

520
00:27:25,479 --> 00:27:26,320
Yuci, why don't I

521
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:27,800
introduce you two?

522
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:28,639
No need.

523
00:27:29,103 --> 00:27:32,515
(Investment Dept 3)

524
00:27:32,553 --> 00:27:33,354
Yuci,

525
00:27:33,919 --> 00:27:35,239
but Mr. Yu asked us

526
00:27:35,239 --> 00:27:36,520
to handle this project together.

527
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:38,159
We'll discuss if something comes up.

528
00:27:38,159 --> 00:27:39,399
Otherwise, let's just
mind our own business.

529
00:27:46,378 --> 00:27:47,499
Do you see what's going on?

530
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:50,080
I don't get it.

531
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:52,840
I see it now.

532
00:27:53,879 --> 00:27:54,479
Rao Yuci

533
00:27:54,479 --> 00:27:56,080
is coming for Bai Liangliang.

534
00:27:56,639 --> 00:27:57,560
Bai Liangliang?

535
00:27:59,840 --> 00:28:01,800
Then, what does Rao Yuci want?

536
00:28:02,465 --> 00:28:03,784
Does she want to sabotage

537
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:05,590
the project Bai Liangliang wants to do?

538
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:07,239
I'm afraid it's not as simple

539
00:28:07,239 --> 00:28:08,239
as just one project.

540
00:28:10,199 --> 00:28:11,719
Whether she's a friend or foe,

541
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,040
let's just wait and see.

542
00:28:51,919 --> 00:28:52,719
Stop hitting me!

543
00:28:55,959 --> 00:28:56,639
Stop it!

544
00:28:56,639 --> 00:28:57,840
I beg you, stop hitting me.

545
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:58,639
Stop it.

546
00:28:58,639 --> 00:28:59,760
Stop it. I beg you.

547
00:29:05,320 --> 00:29:06,919
Hitting you is just the beginning.

548
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:08,520
If you don't pay back the money,

549
00:29:08,879 --> 00:29:10,040
they'll be next.

550
00:29:11,120 --> 00:29:11,919
Let's go.

551
00:29:20,103 --> 00:29:24,140
(Rao Yuci)

552
00:29:30,028 --> 00:29:32,415
(Emergency)

553
00:29:50,399 --> 00:29:51,239
I've already done

554
00:29:51,239 --> 00:29:52,560
exactly as you said.

555
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:55,103
You had me keep
a close eye on Bai Liangliang,

556
00:29:55,479 --> 00:29:56,239
and I even brought

557
00:29:56,239 --> 00:29:57,479
my phone into her office.

558
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:59,239
You know exactly
what she's planning, right?

559
00:29:59,890 --> 00:30:01,919
I still have over ten million
in debt to pay off.

560
00:30:02,919 --> 00:30:04,000
I originally thought

561
00:30:04,479 --> 00:30:05,760
I could take one more gamble

562
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:07,159
to win a bit more money.

563
00:30:07,479 --> 00:30:08,560
That way, my dad

564
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:10,530
could go to a better cancer center
for treatment.

565
00:30:10,978 --> 00:30:12,719
I really didn't expect that.

566
00:30:13,719 --> 00:30:15,000
Please help me.

567
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:17,679
How can I help you?

568
00:30:19,679 --> 00:30:21,560
Help you like I did five years ago?

569
00:30:22,015 --> 00:30:25,199
(Emergency/Outpatient Pharmacy)

570
00:30:25,199 --> 00:30:26,120
Hello, Liangliang.

571
00:30:27,439 --> 00:30:28,919
I just finished my check-up.

572
00:30:30,239 --> 00:30:31,040
Thanks.

573
00:30:31,879 --> 00:30:34,560
They said I have mild depression.

574
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:36,000
I am truly sorry.

575
00:30:36,199 --> 00:30:36,879
And I'm already

576
00:30:36,879 --> 00:30:38,120
working hard to raise the money.

577
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:41,159
We're even going to sell our house.

578
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,521
How about this?

579
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:47,320
I'll leave the property deed with you.

580
00:30:47,853 --> 00:30:49,115
That definitely won't work.

581
00:30:49,399 --> 00:30:50,879
The hospital has its rules.

582
00:30:51,239 --> 00:30:53,479
Your father's fees
have been overdue for a long time.

583
00:30:53,560 --> 00:30:55,520
If you keep this up,
there's nothing we can do.

584
00:30:55,919 --> 00:30:57,239
Your top priority right now

585
00:30:57,239 --> 00:30:58,159
is to raise the money.

586
00:30:58,239 --> 00:30:59,040
You must be quick.

587
00:31:01,828 --> 00:31:04,140
(Move-in ready, near subway,
well-lit, 1.15 million)

588
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,919
Hello, Mr. Zhang.

589
00:31:09,679 --> 00:31:10,479
How about this?

590
00:31:11,280 --> 00:31:14,000
Does one million work for you?

591
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,190
I'll lower the price a bit more.

592
00:31:16,878 --> 00:31:17,959
Li Mingxuan!

593
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:23,360
Where is the money?

594
00:31:25,978 --> 00:31:26,779
What money?

595
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:28,150
What do you mean by "what money"?

596
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:30,399
You have the USB drive
for the company account!

597
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:32,190
Where is the one million
in reserve funds?

598
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,040
I'm talking to you!

599
00:31:36,210 --> 00:31:37,239
I'm the one who moved it.

600
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,159
Part of the business investigation

601
00:31:42,159 --> 00:31:43,990
for Chenyang Appliances
needs to be outsourced.

602
00:31:44,439 --> 00:31:46,760
So I had Mingxuan
transfer that money to me.

603
00:31:46,959 --> 00:31:47,760
Well,

604
00:31:48,239 --> 00:31:50,679
don't you think you should have
discussed it with us first?

605
00:31:51,199 --> 00:31:52,760
Besides, it shouldn't cost that much.

606
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,719
I'll pay it back
within the next couple of days.

607
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:57,671
It's fine as long as it's cleared up.

608
00:31:58,399 --> 00:31:59,479
We're all on the same team.

609
00:32:00,719 --> 00:32:01,520
Back to work.

610
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:07,520
Yuci, thank you so much.

611
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:09,320
You're going through
a tough time right now.

612
00:32:09,330 --> 00:32:12,000
Getting medical treatment
for the elderly is definitely a top priority.

613
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:12,959
As your friend,

614
00:32:12,959 --> 00:32:14,280
it's only right that I help you.

615
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:15,439
This million

616
00:32:16,639 --> 00:32:18,159
really is a godsend.

617
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,719
I will pay you back as soon as possible.

618
00:32:21,919 --> 00:32:22,719
Bye-bye.

619
00:32:23,120 --> 00:32:23,919
Bye-bye.

620
00:32:24,679 --> 00:32:25,719
Take care, Yuci.

621
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:36,800
Hello.

622
00:32:37,128 --> 00:32:37,967
Mr. Zhang.

623
00:32:39,679 --> 00:32:40,479
No, no.

624
00:32:41,159 --> 00:32:42,080
What I mean is,

625
00:32:43,159 --> 00:32:44,520
I'm not selling the house anymore.

626
00:32:48,479 --> 00:32:49,280
Yuci,

627
00:32:50,199 --> 00:32:51,320
sorry.

628
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,199
You can blame me all you want.

629
00:32:54,399 --> 00:32:55,399
You can punish me

630
00:32:55,399 --> 00:32:56,639
or curse me however you like.

631
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,280
But can you please help my parents?

632
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,080
Those loan sharks said

633
00:33:01,439 --> 00:33:02,800
that if I don't pay them back,

634
00:33:03,919 --> 00:33:05,639
they'll go after my parents next.

635
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,879
You know my dad

636
00:33:09,565 --> 00:33:10,515
is...

637
00:33:14,479 --> 00:33:15,560
I can help you.

638
00:33:19,360 --> 00:33:20,479
But you need to...

639
00:33:22,879 --> 00:33:24,239
Something happened!

640
00:33:24,239 --> 00:33:24,959
What's wrong?

641
00:33:25,479 --> 00:33:26,280
A jumper!

642
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,159
Don't come over!

643
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:28,879
Stay back!

644
00:33:42,439 --> 00:33:43,439
What should we do?

645
00:33:44,159 --> 00:33:45,040
I don't know either.

646
00:33:46,719 --> 00:33:47,520
Yuci,

647
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:49,360
I've already done

648
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,719
exactly what Bai Liangliang said.

649
00:33:51,520 --> 00:33:52,320
You told me

650
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:54,040
that as long as I cooperated with her,

651
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,239
you would help me, right?

652
00:33:55,439 --> 00:33:57,239
I need you to transfer
the rest of the money

653
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:58,679
to me right now.

654
00:33:58,679 --> 00:33:59,320
Okay.

655
00:33:59,515 --> 00:34:00,978
(Phone, Bai Liangliang)

656
00:34:01,028 --> 00:34:02,015
(Bai Liangliang)

657
00:34:02,919 --> 00:34:03,719
Liangliang,

658
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:06,199
I want to confirm
with you one more time.

659
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:09,120
If I tell Mr. Li

660
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:11,880
that Mr. Jiang caused Li Qiang's death,

661
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,600
you'll help me pay off my debt?

662
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,239
Yes.

663
00:34:15,239 --> 00:34:15,960
Good.

664
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,480
Transfer half to me now.

665
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,239
Fine. No problem.

666
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,480
Ms. Bai,

667
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:25,630
Manager Li is on the observation deck,
threatening to jump.

668
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,040
He also said he wants to see Mr. Li.

669
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:29,359
Then call Mr. Li.

670
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,660
It's a matter of life and death.

671
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:31,799
Yes, got it.

672
00:34:34,560 --> 00:34:35,679
Don't come over! Stand back!

673
00:34:35,679 --> 00:34:36,600
Careful.

674
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,440
Stay back!

675
00:34:37,450 --> 00:34:38,520
Li Mingxuan, don't do anything rash!

676
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:39,319
Back up!

677
00:34:39,560 --> 00:34:40,639
I'm going to jump!

678
00:34:40,679 --> 00:34:41,520
We're backing up.

679
00:34:41,520 --> 00:34:42,639
Get Mr. Li and Mr. Jiang

680
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:43,239
over here.

681
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:45,070
I have something very important
to tell them.

682
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:45,759
Back up.

683
00:34:45,759 --> 00:34:46,480
Dongchao.

684
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:47,960
Mr. Li.

685
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:50,470
First thing this morning,
something so big happened at Lysen.

686
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:52,159
People are already calling me about it.

687
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:53,560
Why did you still come here?

688
00:34:59,040 --> 00:34:59,839
Mr. Li,

689
00:35:00,799 --> 00:35:01,759
I am responsible

690
00:35:03,319 --> 00:35:04,560
for Li Qiang's death.

691
00:35:07,639 --> 00:35:08,560
When I first found out

692
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,839
that he was gambling,

693
00:35:10,759 --> 00:35:12,359
I met with him privately a few times.

694
00:35:13,450 --> 00:35:14,880
I just wanted to try to persuade him

695
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,839
to stop in my own way.

696
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:18,159
But as you know,

697
00:35:18,679 --> 00:35:19,400
a gambling addict

698
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:21,040
won't listen to reason.

699
00:35:22,520 --> 00:35:23,900
I am responsible for lax management

700
00:35:24,159 --> 00:35:25,520
and for not showing enough concern.

701
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:29,600
I sincerely ask for your forgiveness.

702
00:35:33,719 --> 00:35:35,159
Li Qiang was your child,

703
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:39,120
just as Lysen is to both of us.

704
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,990
Now someone is standing
on the roof of Lysen,

705
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:43,199
simply to create a spectacle,

706
00:35:43,199 --> 00:35:44,279
smear our names,

707
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:46,359
and drive a wedge between us.

708
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,759
The biggest victim of this farce

709
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:51,679
isn't me, Jiang Dongchao,

710
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,359
nor is it you, Mr. Li.

711
00:35:55,520 --> 00:35:56,960
It's Lysen, which we have

712
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:57,960
worked so hard to build.

713
00:36:01,239 --> 00:36:02,040
Back up!

714
00:36:02,239 --> 00:36:03,279
I'm going to jump!

715
00:36:03,279 --> 00:36:04,239
I'm really jumping!

716
00:36:04,639 --> 00:36:05,440
Li Mingxuan.

717
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:12,400
This is not a joke.

718
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,319
Don't go over there.

719
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:16,600
He and I are old friends.

720
00:36:17,319 --> 00:36:18,279
Don't come any closer.

721
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,120
I'm really going to jump.

722
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,719
I'm only one step away.

723
00:36:23,359 --> 00:36:24,759
Don't come any closer.

724
00:36:25,639 --> 00:36:26,440
Stop.

725
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:28,719
Don't move.

726
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:29,960
Step back a bit further.

727
00:36:30,639 --> 00:36:32,279
This act is about to become real.

728
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:34,378
(Bai Liangliang)

729
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,679
Li Mingxuan, you really haven't changed.

730
00:36:48,799 --> 00:36:49,920
You begged me

731
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,440
while also begging Bai Liangliang.

732
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:54,400
Someone told me three years ago

733
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:56,920
that cowardice
is your survival mechanism.

734
00:36:59,759 --> 00:37:00,639
Right, Liangliang?

735
00:37:00,678 --> 00:37:02,640
(Phone, Bai Liangliang)

736
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,600
Yuci, you can't keep doing this.

737
00:37:06,839 --> 00:37:08,880
Didn't something happen
to Mingxuan's father?

738
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,279
Of course we have to help.

739
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:12,120
He didn't explicitly ask us for help,

740
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,719
which means he still has a way out.

741
00:37:13,719 --> 00:37:15,920
As a friend, when you see it,
you have to do something.

742
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:17,880
You can't let your kindness be abused.

743
00:37:18,239 --> 00:37:20,440
Especially by a coward.

744
00:37:20,990 --> 00:37:22,719
Cowardice isn't quite

745
00:37:22,719 --> 00:37:24,040
what it seems on the surface.

746
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:24,639
Cowardice

747
00:37:24,639 --> 00:37:26,679
is just his way of surviving.

748
00:37:30,279 --> 00:37:31,239
Just come down.

749
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:34,560
A person as cowardly

750
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:35,719
and selfish as you

751
00:37:38,199 --> 00:37:39,679
doesn't have the courage to die.

752
00:37:40,639 --> 00:37:42,199
You only use your cowardice

753
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:44,239
to get others to help you

754
00:37:44,239 --> 00:37:45,719
clean up your messes.

755
00:37:45,719 --> 00:37:46,920
And you'll just keep hiding

756
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:47,960
behind that cowardice

757
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,960
and continue living selfishly.

758
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:50,920
Am I right?

759
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:55,960
Everyone quiet. Don't go over.

760
00:37:56,839 --> 00:37:57,639
Don't move.

761
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:58,920
I am a coward.

762
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:00,319
I am selfish.

763
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,759
I have no shame.

764
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,239
Pitiable people

765
00:38:03,239 --> 00:38:05,400
truly do have detestable sides.

766
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:09,480
My detestable side lies in the fact

767
00:38:11,159 --> 00:38:11,920
that my kindness

768
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,600
was trampled upon,

769
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:14,960
played with, and exploited,

770
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:17,319
yet I was unaware of it.

771
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,639
The strong always think

772
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:21,199
they will be hurt by someone stronger.

773
00:38:21,199 --> 00:38:22,440
That's not true.

774
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,400
Those who can hurt the strong

775
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:26,199
are often the most cowardly people.

776
00:38:26,359 --> 00:38:28,080
Your detestable side

777
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:32,880
is that you beg others
without any dignity

778
00:38:33,528 --> 00:38:35,209
to fulfill your own desires.

779
00:38:37,719 --> 00:38:38,719
What else could I do?

780
00:38:39,799 --> 00:38:41,159
I don't have your brains.

781
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:43,560
I don't have Bai Muran's

782
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:44,520
family background.

783
00:38:45,700 --> 00:38:47,000
And I'm not like Bai Liangliang,

784
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,480
who has so many tricks.

785
00:38:49,239 --> 00:38:50,560
I wanted to succeed, too.

786
00:38:51,428 --> 00:38:53,382
I wanted people to respect me.

787
00:38:54,199 --> 00:38:55,759
You can't even imagine

788
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:58,279
the malice born of cowardice.

789
00:38:58,679 --> 00:38:59,639
Do you understand?

790
00:39:02,178 --> 00:39:03,239
(Bai Liangliang)
When you helped Bai Liangliang

791
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:03,920
and her partner

792
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,159
hurt me,

793
00:39:06,319 --> 00:39:08,159
did you ever think
about how much I suffered?

794
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:09,960
Why didn't you tell me?

795
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,600
I'll come back and see you.

796
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,159
Calm down!

797
00:39:13,628 --> 00:39:16,865
♪You could pray, but won't be saved♪

798
00:39:17,679 --> 00:39:18,560
I was wrong.

799
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:21,199
I shouldn't
have listened to Bai Liangliang.

800
00:39:21,199 --> 00:39:22,920
I shouldn't have helped them hurt you.

801
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:24,210
I'm begging you.

802
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,279
I'll do whatever you want.

803
00:39:25,279 --> 00:39:26,159
I'm begging you.

804
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,440
Please, I'm begging you.

805
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:29,279
Please, please.

806
00:39:31,279 --> 00:39:32,400
I can help you.

807
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,799
But this time, there are conditions.

808
00:39:39,953 --> 00:39:41,120
The condition is...

809
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:44,828
(Bai Liangliang)
♪From the start to the end you're damned♪

810
00:39:44,915 --> 00:39:49,540
♪I'm coming back untamed♪

811
00:39:51,159 --> 00:39:53,319
The number
you have dialed is powered off.

812
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:00,600
Go and experience

813
00:40:01,719 --> 00:40:03,199
a life of failure.

814
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:11,910
=Episode 2=
(The Evil of Cowardice)

815
00:40:12,460 --> 00:40:14,900
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

816
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:21,100
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

817
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:25,060
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

818
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:29,580
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

819
00:40:29,580 --> 00:40:37,100
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

820
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:41,020
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

821
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:45,060
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

822
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:48,580
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

823
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:52,540
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

824
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:56,700
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

825
00:40:56,700 --> 00:41:00,900
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

826
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:04,700
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

827
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:08,780
♪Keep walking through the light♪

828
00:41:08,780 --> 00:41:12,980
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

829
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:19,300
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

830
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:43,060
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

831
00:41:43,060 --> 00:41:46,900
♪An apology that came too late♪

832
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:51,540
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

833
00:41:51,620 --> 00:41:59,020
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

834
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:03,100
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

835
00:42:03,100 --> 00:42:07,180
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

836
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:11,180
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

837
00:42:11,180 --> 00:42:14,940
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

838
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:19,140
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

839
00:42:19,140 --> 00:42:23,300
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

840
00:42:23,300 --> 00:42:27,020
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

841
00:42:27,020 --> 00:42:31,060
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

842
00:42:31,060 --> 00:42:35,100
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

843
00:42:35,100 --> 00:42:41,300
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
